                "inputAnchors": [],
                "inputs": {
                    "llmModel": "chatZhipuAI",
                    "llmMessages": [
                        {
                            "role": "system",
                            "content": "<p>你是一名资深职场报告撰写专家，擅长撰写周报、月报、项目汇报和调研报告。请基于用户提供的信息产出结构清晰、重点突出、数据导向的中文报告初稿。表达要专业、克制、可落地，不夸大，不使用「最」「第一」「国家级」等绝对化表述；对未提供的数据要用“可补充数据”或“待确认”提示，不臆造事实。</p>"
                        },
                        {
                            "role": "user",
                            "content": "<p>请基于以下表单信息撰写一份中文报告：</p><p>报告类型：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.reportType\" data-label=\"$form.reportType\">{{ $form.reportType }}</span></p><p>主题：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.topic\" data-label=\"$form.topic\">{{ $form.topic }}</span></p><p>汇报对象：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.audience\" data-label=\"$form.audience\">{{ $form.audience }}</span></p><p>关键要点：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.keyPoints\" data-label=\"$form.keyPoints\">{{ $form.keyPoints }}</span></p><p>时间范围：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.period\" data-label=\"$form.period\">{{ $form.period }}</span></p><p>目标字数：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.wordCount\" data-label=\"$form.wordCount\">{{ $form.wordCount }}</span></p><p>要求：请先给出适合汇报对象的标题和摘要，再按逻辑章节展开正文。每个章节需要有清晰小标题、正文内容和要点列表；最后给出下一步行动建议。若输入信息不足，请明确标注需要补充的数据，不要虚构具体数字或事实。</p>"
                        }
                    ],
                    "llmEnableMemory": false,
                    "llmReturnResponseAs": "userMessage",
                    "llmStructuredOutput": [
                        {
                            "key": "title",
                            "type": "string",
                            "enumValues": "",
                            "jsonSchema": "",
                            "description": "报告标题"
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "summary",
                            "type": "string",
                            "enumValues": "",
                            "jsonSchema": "",
                            "description": "面向汇报对象的摘要，概括重点结论与价值"
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "sections",
                            "type": "jsonArray",
                            "enumValues": "",
                            "jsonSchema": "{\n    \"heading\": {\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"description\": \"章节标题\"\n    },\n    \"content\": {\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"description\": \"章节正文\"\n    },\n    \"bullets\": {\n        \"type\": \"array\",\n        \"items\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n        },\n        \"description\": \"章节要点列表\"\n    }\n}",
                            "description": "报告正文分节，每节包含标题、正文和要点列表"
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "nextSteps",
                            "type": "stringArray",
                            "enumValues": "",
                            "jsonSchema": "",
                            "description": "后续行动、补充材料或需要确认的事项"
                        }
                    ],
                    "llmUpdateState": "",
                    "llmModelConfig": {
                        "cache": "",
                        "modelName": "glm-4.5",
                        "customModelName": "",
                        "temperature": 0.8,
                        "streaming": true,
                        "maxTokens": "",
                        "topP": "",
                        "frequencyPenalty": "",
                        "presencePenalty": "",
                        "timeout": "",
                        "stopSequence": "",
                        "baseOptions": "",
                        "llmModel": "chatZhipuAI"
                    }
